import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-event-modal',
  templateUrl: './event-modal.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./event-modal.component.scss'],
})
export class EventModalComponent  implements OnInit {

  constructor() { }

  ngOnInit() {}

}
<ion-header>
  <ion-toolbar>
    <ion-title>
      My Modal
    </ion-title>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

<ion-content>
  <ion-card>
    <ion-card-header>
      <ion-card-title>Modal Content</ion-card-title>
    </ion-card-header>
    <ion-card-content>
      This is the content of my modal.
    </ion-card-content>
  </ion-card>
  <ion-button expand="full" (click)="dismiss()">Close Modal</ion-button>
</ion-content>
